0	and inaccessible the arabian drouth 
0	here nineveh of length within her wall
0	several days journey built by ninus old 
0	of that first golden monarchy the seat 
0	and seat of salmanassar whose success
0	israel in long captivity still mourns 
0	there babylon the wonder of all tongues 
0	as ancient but rebuilt by him who twice
0	judah and all thy father david s house
