0	the great seleucia nisibis and there
0	turning with easy eye thou may st behold 
0	all these the parthian now some ages past
0	by great arsaces led who founded first
0	that empire under his dominion holds 
0	from the luxurious kings of antioch won 
0	and just in time thou com st to have a view
