0	his thousands in what martial equipage
0	they issue forth steel bows and shafts their arms 
0	of equal dread in flight or in pursuit 
0	all horsemen in which fight they most excel 
0	see how in warlike muster they appear 
0	in rhombs and wedges and half moons and wings 
0	he looked and saw what numbers numberless
0	the city gates outpoured light armed troops
0	in coats of mail and military pride 
0	in mail their horses clad yet fleet and strong 
0	prauncing their riders bore the flower and choice
