0	how quick they wheeled and flying behind them shot
0	sharp sleet of arrowy showers against the face
0	of their pursuers and overcame by flight 
0	the field all iron cast a gleaming brown 
0	nor wanted clouds of foot nor on each horn 
0	cuirassiers all in steel for standing fight 
0	chariots or elephants indorsed with towers
0	of archers nor of labouring pioners
