0	this offer sets before thee to deliver 
0	these if from servitude thou shalt restore
0	to their inheritance then nor till then 
0	thou on the throne of david in full glory 
0	shalt reign and rome or caesar not need fear 
0	to whom our saviour answered thus unmoved 
0	 much ostentation vain of fleshly arm
0	and fragile arms much instrument of war 
0	long in preparing soon to nothing brought 
0	before mine eyes thou hast set and in my ear
0	vented much policy and projects deep
