0	appeared and serried shields in thick array
0	of depth immeasurable anon they move
0	in perfect phalanx to the dorian mood
0	of flutes and soft recorders such as raised
0	to height of noblest temper heroes old
0	arming to battle and instead of rage
0	deliberate valour breathed firm and unmoved
0	with dread of death to flight or foul retreat 
0	nor wanting power to mitigate and swage
0	with solemn touches troubled thoughts and chase
