0	of dreadful length and dazzling arms in guise
0	of warriors old with ordered spear and shield 
0	awaiting what command their mighty chief
0	had to impose he through the armed files
0	darts his experienced eye and soon traverse
0	the whole battalion views their order due 
0	their visages and stature as of gods 
