0	celestial spirits in bondage nor th abyss
0	long under darkness cover but these thoughts
0	full counsel must mature peace is despaired 
0	for who can think submission war then war
0	open or understood must be resolved 
0	he spake and to confirm his words outflew
0	millions of flaming swords drawn from the thighs
