0	satan exalted sat by merit raised
0	to that bad eminence and from despair
0	thus high uplifted beyond hope aspires
0	beyond thus high insatiate to pursue
0	vain war with heaven and by success untaught 
0	his proud imaginations thus displayed 
0	for since no deep within her gulf can hold
0	immortal vigour though oppressed and fallen 
0	i give not heaven for lost from this descent
0	celestial virtues rising will appear
0	more glorious and more dread than from no fall 
0	and trust themselves to fear no second fate 
0	me though just right and the fixed laws of heaven 
0	did first create your leader next free choice
0	with what besides in council or in fight
0	hath been achieved of merit yet this loss 
0	thus far at least recovered hath much more
0	established in a safe unenvied throne 
0	yielded with full consent the happier state
0	in heaven which follows dignity might draw
0	envy from each inferior but who here
0	will envy whom the highest place exposes
0	foremost to stand against the thunderer s aim
0	your bulwark and condemns to greatest share
0	of endless pain where there is then no good
0	for which to strive no strife can grow up there
0	from faction for none sure will claim in hell
0	precedence none whose portion is so small
0	of present pain that with ambitious mind
0	will covet more with this advantage then 
0	to union and firm faith and firm accord 
0	more than can be in heaven we now return
0	to claim our just inheritance of old 
0	surer to prosper than prosperity
0	could have assured us and by what best way 
0	whether of open war or covert guile 
