0	we sunk thus low th ascent is easy then 
0	th event is feared should we again provoke
0	our stronger some worse way his wrath may find
0	to our destruction if there be in hell
0	fear to be worse destroyed what can be worse
0	than to dwell here driven out from bliss condemned
0	in this abhorred deep to utter woe 
0	where pain of unextinguishable fire
0	must exercise us without hope of end
0	the vassals of his anger when the scourge
0	inexorably and the torturing hour 
0	calls us to penance more destroyed than thus 
0	we should be quite abolished and expire 
0	what fear we then what doubt we to incense
0	his utmost ire which to the height enraged 
0	will either quite consume us and reduce
0	to nothing this essential happier far
0	than miserable to have eternal being 
0	or if our substance be indeed divine 
0	and cannot cease to be we are at worst
0	on this side nothing and by proof we feel
0	our power sufficient to disturb his heaven 
0	and with perpetual inroads to alarm 
0	though inaccessible his fatal throne 
0	which if not victory is yet revenge 
0	he ended frowning and his look denounced
0	desperate revenge and battle dangerous
0	to less than gods on th other side up rose
0	belial in act more graceful and humane 
0	a fairer person lost not heaven he seemed
0	for dignity composed and high exploit 
0	but all was false and hollow though his tongue
0	dropped manna and could make the worse appear
