0	did not dissuade me most and seem to cast
0	ominous conjecture on the whole success 
0	when he who most excels in fact of arms 
0	in what he counsels and in what excels
0	mistrustful grounds his courage on despair
0	and utter dissolution as the scope
0	of all his aim after some dire revenge 
0	first what revenge the towers of heaven are filled
0	with armed watch that render all access
0	impregnable oft on the bordering deep
0	encamp their legions or with obscure wing
0	scout far and wide into the realm of night 
0	scorning surprise or could we break our way
0	by force and at our heels all hell should rise
0	with blackest insurrection to confound
0	heaven s purest light yet our great enemy 
0	all incorruptible would on his throne
