0	mustering their rage and heaven resembles hell 
0	as he our darkness cannot we his light
0	imitate when we please this desert soil
0	wants not her hidden lustre gems and gold 
0	nor want we skill or art from whence to raise
0	magnificence and what can heaven show more 
0	our torments also may in length of time 
0	become our elements these piercing fires
