0	the tempting stream with one small drop to lose
0	in sweet forgetfulness all pain and woe 
0	all in one moment and so near the brink 
0	but fate withstands and to oppose th attempt 
0	medusa with gorgonian terror guards
0	the ford and of itself the water flies
0	all taste of living wight as once it fled
0	the lip of tantalus thus roving on
