0	three iron three of adamantine rock 
0	impenetrable impaled with circling fire 
0	yet unconsumed before the gates there sat
0	on either side a formidable shape 
0	the one seemed woman to the waist and fair 
0	but ended foul in many a scaly fold 
0	voluminous and vast a serpent armed
0	with mortal sting about her middle round
