0	myself expose with lonely steps to tread
0	th unfounded deep and through the void immense
0	to search with wandering quest a place foretold
0	should be and by concurring signs ere now
0	created vast and round a place of bliss
0	in the purlieus of heaven and therein placed
0	a race of upstart creatures to supply
