0	with odours there ye shall be fed and filled
0	immeasurably all things shall be your prey 
0	he ceased for both seemed highly pleased and death
0	grinned horrible a ghastly smile to hear
0	his famine should be filled and blessed his maw
0	destined to that good hour no less rejoiced
