0	 the key of this infernal pit by due
0	and by command of heaven s all powerful king 
0	i keep by him forbidden to unlock
0	these adamantine gates against all force
0	death ready stands to interpose his dart 
0	fearless to be o ermatched by living might 
0	but what owe i to his commands above 
0	who hates me and hath hither thrust me down
0	into this gloom of tartarus profound 
0	to sit in hateful office here confined 
0	inhabitant of heaven and heavenly born 
