0	and shook his plumes that heavenly fragrance filled
0	the circuit wide straight knew him all the bands
0	of angels under watch and to his state 
0	and to his message high in honour rise 
0	for on some message high they guessed him bound 
0	their glittering tents he passed and now is come
0	into the blissful field through groves of myrrh 
0	and flowering odours cassia nard and balm 
0	a wilderness of sweets for nature here
0	wantoned as in her prime and played at will
0	her virgin fancies pouring forth more sweet 
0	wild above rule or art enormous bliss 
0	him through the spicy forest onward come
0	adam discerned as in the door he sat
