0	at which command the powers militant 
0	that stood for heaven in mighty quadrate joined
0	of union irresistible moved on
0	in silence their bright legions to the sound
0	of instrumental harmony that breathed
0	heroick ardour to adventurous deeds
0	under their god like leaders in the cause
0	of god and his messiah on they move
0	indissolubly firm nor obvious hill 
0	nor straitening vale nor wood nor stream divides
