0	with furious expedition for they weened
0	that self same day by fight or by surprise 
0	to win the mount of god and on his throne
0	to set the envier of his state the proud
0	aspirer but their thoughts proved fond and vain
0	in the mid way though strange to us it seemed
0	at first that angel should with angel war 
0	and in fierce hosting meet who wont to meet
0	so oft in festivals of joy and love
0	unanimous as sons of one great sire 
