0	was never arms on armour clashing brayed
0	horrible discord and the madding wheels
0	of brazen chariots raged dire was the noise
0	of conflict over head the dismal hiss
0	of fiery darts in flaming vollies flew 
0	and flying vaulted either host with fire 
0	so under fiery cope together rushed
0	both battles main with ruinous assault
0	and inextinguishable rage all heaven
0	resounded and had earth been then all earth
0	had to her center shook what wonder when
0	millions of fierce encountering angels fought
0	on either side the least of whom could wield
0	these elements and arm him with the force
0	of all their regions how much more of power
0	army against army numberless to raise
0	dreadful combustion warring and disturb 
0	though not destroy their happy native seat 
0	from his strong hold of heaven high over ruled
0	and limited their might though numbered such
0	as each divided legion might have seemed
0	a numerous host in strength each armed hand
0	a legion led in fight yet leader seemed
0	each warriour single as in chief expert
0	when to advance or stand or turn the sway
0	of battle open when and when to close
0	the ridges of grim war no thought of flight 
0	none of retreat no unbecoming deed
0	that argued fear each on himself relied 
0	as only in his arm the moment lay
0	of victory deeds of eternal fame
0	were done but infinite for wide was spread
0	that war and various sometimes on firm ground
0	a standing fight then soaring on main wing 
0	tormented all the air all air seemed then
0	conflicting fire long time in even scale
0	the battle hung till satan who that day
0	prodigious power had shown and met in arms
0	no equal ranging through the dire attack
0	of fighting seraphim confused at length
0	saw where the sword of michael smote and felled
0	squadrons at once with huge two handed sway
0	brandished aloft the horrid edge came down
0	wide wasting such destruction to withstand
0	he hasted and opposed the rocky orb
0	of tenfold adamant his ample shield 
0	a vast circumference at his approach
0	the great arch angel from his warlike toil
0	surceased and glad as hoping here to end
0	intestine war in heaven the arch foe subdued
0	or captive dragged in chains with hostile frown
0	and visage all inflamed first thus began 
0	author of evil unknown till thy revolt 
0	unnamed in heaven now plenteous as thou seest
0	these acts of hateful strife hateful to all 
0	though heaviest by just measure on thyself 
0	and thy adherents how hast thou disturbed
0	heaven s blessed peace and into nature brought
0	misery uncreated till the crime
0	of thy rebellion how hast thou instilled
0	thy malice into thousands once upright
0	and faithful now proved false but think not here
0	to trouble holy rest heaven casts thee out
0	from all her confines heaven the seat of bliss 
0	brooks not the works of violence and war 
0	hence then and evil go with thee along 
0	thy offspring to the place of evil hell 
0	thou and thy wicked crew there mingle broils 
0	ere this avenging sword begin thy doom 
0	or some more sudden vengeance winged from god 
0	precipitate thee with augmented pain 
0	so spake the prince of angels to whom thus
0	the adversary nor think thou with wind
0	of aery threats to awe whom yet with deeds
0	thou canst not hast thou turned the least of these
0	to flight or if to fall but that they rise
0	unvanquished easier to transact with me
0	that thou shouldst hope imperious and with threats
0	to chase me hence err not that so shall end
0	the strife which thou callest evil but we style
0	the strife of glory which we mean to win 
0	or turn this heaven itself into the hell
0	thou fablest here however to dwell free 
0	if not to reign mean while thy utmost force 
0	and join him named almighty to thy aid 
0	i fly not but have sought thee far and nigh 
0	they ended parle and both addressed for fight
0	unspeakable for who though with the tongue
0	of angels can relate or to what things
0	liken on earth conspicuous that may lift
0	human imagination to such highth
0	of godlike power for likest gods they seemed 
0	stood they or moved in stature motion arms 
0	fit to decide the empire of great heaven 
0	now waved their fiery swords and in the air
0	made horrid circles two broad suns their shields
0	blazed opposite while expectation stood
0	in horrour from each hand with speed retired 
0	where erst was thickest fight the angelick throng 
0	and left large field unsafe within the wind
0	of such commotion such as to set forth
0	great things by small if nature s concord broke 
0	among the constellations war were sprung 
0	two planets rushing from aspect malign
0	of fiercest opposition in mid sky
0	should combat and their jarring spheres confound 
0	together both with next to almighty arm
0	up lifted imminent one stroke they aimed
0	that might determine and not need repeat 
0	as not of power at once nor odds appeared
0	in might or swift prevention but the sword
0	of michael from the armoury of god
0	was given him tempered so that neither keen
0	nor solid might resist that edge it met
0	the sword of satan with steep force to smite
0	descending and in half cut sheer nor staid 
0	but with swift wheel reverse deep entering shared
0	all his right side then satan first knew pain 
0	and writhed him to and fro convolved so sore
0	the griding sword with discontinuous wound
0	passed through him but the ethereal substance closed 
0	not long divisible and from the gash
0	a stream of necturous humour issuing flowed
0	sanguine such as celestial spirits may bleed 
0	and all his armour stained ere while so bright 
0	forthwith on all sides to his aid was run
0	by angels many and strong who interposed
0	defence while others bore him on their shields
0	back to his chariot where it stood retired
0	from off the files of war there they him laid
0	gnashing for anguish and despite and shame 
0	to find himself not matchless and his pride
0	humbled by such rebuke so far beneath
0	his confidence to equal god in power 
0	yet soon he healed for spirits that live throughout
0	vital in every part not as frail man
0	in entrails heart of head liver or reins 
0	cannot but by annihilating die 
0	nor in their liquid texture mortal wound
0	receive no more than can the fluid air 
0	all heart they live all head all eye all ear 
0	all intellect all sense and as they please 
0	they limb themselves and colour shape or size
0	assume as likes them best condense or rare 
0	mean while in other parts like deeds deserved
0	memorial where the might of gabriel fought 
0	and with fierce ensigns pierced the deep array
0	of moloch furious king who him defied 
0	and at his chariot wheels to drag him bound
0	threatened nor from the holy one of heaven
0	refrained his tongue blasphemous but anon
0	down cloven to the waist with shattered arms
0	and uncouth pain fled bellowing on each wing
0	uriel and raphael his vaunting foe 
0	though huge and in a rock of diamond armed 
0	two potent thrones that to be less than gods
0	disdained but meaner thoughts learned in their flight 
0	mangled with ghastly wounds through plate and mail 
0	nor stood unmindful abdiel to annoy
0	the atheist crew but with redoubled blow
0	ariel and arioch and the violence
0	of ramiel scorched and blasted overthrew 
0	i might relate of thousands and their names
0	eternize here on earth but those elect
0	angels contented with their fame in heaven 
0	seek not the praise of men the other sort 
0	in might though wonderous and in acts of war 
0	nor of renown less eager yet by doom
0	cancelled from heaven and sacred memory 
0	nameless in dark oblivion let them dwell 
0	for strength from truth divided and from just 
0	illaudable nought merits but dispraise
0	and ignominy yet to glory aspires
0	vain glorious and through infamy seeks fame 
0	therefore eternal silence be their doom 
0	and now their mightiest quelled the battle swerved 
0	with many an inroad gored deformed rout
0	entered and foul disorder all the ground
0	with shivered armour strown and on a heap
0	chariot and charioteer lay overturned 
0	and fiery foaming steeds what stood recoiled
0	o er wearied through the faint satanick host
0	defensive scarce or with pale fear surprised 
0	then first with fear surprised and sense of pain 
0	fled ignominious to such evil brought
0	by sin of disobedience till that hour
0	not liable to fear or flight or pain 
0	far otherwise the inviolable saints 
0	in cubick phalanx firm advanced entire 
0	invulnerable impenetrably armed 
0	such high advantages their innocence
0	gave them above their foes not to have sinned 
0	not to have disobeyed in fight they stood
0	unwearied unobnoxious to be pained
0	by wound though from their place by violence moved 
0	now night her course began and over heaven
0	inducing darkness grateful truce imposed 
0	and silence on the odious din of war 
0	under her cloudy covert both retired 
0	victor and vanquished on the foughten field
0	michael and his angels prevalent
0	encamping placed in guard their watches round 
0	cherubick waving fires on the other part 
