0	far in the dark dislodged and void of rest 
0	his potentates to council called by night 
0	and in the midst thus undismayed began 
0	o now in danger tried now known in arms
0	not to be overpowered companions dear 
0	found worthy not of liberty alone 
0	too mean pretence but what we more affect 
0	honour dominion glory and renown 
0	who have sustained one day in doubtful fight 
0	 and if one day why not eternal days 
0	what heaven s lord had powerfullest to send
0	against us from about his throne and judged
0	sufficient to subdue us to his will 
0	but proves not so then fallible it seems 
0	of future we may deem him though till now
0	omniscient thought true is less firmly armed 
0	some disadvantage we endured and pain 
0	till now not known but known as soon contemned 
0	since now we find this our empyreal form
0	incapable of mortal injury 
0	imperishable and though pierced with wound 
0	soon closing and by native vigour healed 
0	of evil then so small as easy think
0	the remedy perhaps more valid arms 
0	weapons more violent when next we meet 
0	may serve to better us and worse our foes 
0	or equal what between us made the odds 
0	in nature none if other hidden cause
0	left them superiour while we can preserve
0	unhurt our minds and understanding sound 
0	due search and consultation will disclose 
0	he sat and in the assembly next upstood
0	nisroch of principalities the prime 
0	as one he stood escaped from cruel fight 
0	sore toiled his riven arms to havock hewn 
0	and cloudy in aspect thus answering spake 
