0	with heaven s ray and tempered they shoot forth
0	so beauteous opening to the ambient light 
0	these in their dark nativity the deep
0	shall yield us pregnant with infernal flame 
0	which into hollow engines long and round 
0	thick rammed at the other bore with touch of fire
0	dilated and infuriate shall send forth
