0	effulgence of my glory son beloved 
0	son in whose face invisible is beheld
0	visibly what by deity i am 
0	and in whose hand what by decree i do 
0	second omnipotence two days are past 
0	two days as we compute the days of heaven 
0	since michael and his powers went forth to tame
0	these disobedient sore hath been their fight 
0	as likeliest was when two such foes met armed 
0	for to themselves i left them and thou knowest 
0	equal in their creation they were formed 
0	save what sin hath impaired which yet hath wrought
0	insensibly for i suspend their doom 
0	whence in perpetual fight they needs must last
0	endless and no solution will be found 
0	war wearied hath performed what war can do 
0	and to disordered rage let loose the reins
0	with mountains as with weapons armed which makes
0	wild work in heaven and dangerous to the main 
0	two days are therefore past the third is thine 
0	for thee i have ordained it and thus far
0	have suffered that the glory may be thine
0	of ending this great war since none but thou
0	can end it into thee such virtue and grace
0	immense i have transfused that all may know
0	in heaven and hell thy power above compare 
0	and this perverse commotion governed thus 
0	to manifest thee worthiest to be heir
0	of all things to be heir and to be king
0	by sacred unction thy deserved right 
0	go then thou mightiest in thy father s might 
0	ascend my chariot guide the rapid wheels
0	that shake heaven s basis bring forth all my war 
0	my bow and thunder my almighty arms
0	gird on and sword upon thy puissant thigh 
0	pursue these sons of darkness drive them out
0	from all heaven s bounds into the utter deep 
0	there let them learn as likes them to despise
0	god and messiah his anointed king 
