0	wisdom thy sister and with her didst play
0	in presence of the almighty father pleased
0	with thy celestial song up led by thee
0	into the heaven of heavens i have presumed 
0	an earthly guest and drawn empyreal air 
0	thy tempering with like safety guided down
0	return me to my native element 
0	lest from this flying steed unreined as once
0	bellerophon though from a lower clime 
