0	she disappeared and left me dark i waked
0	to find her or for ever to deplore
0	her loss and other pleasures all abjure 
0	when out of hope behold her not far off 
0	such as i saw her in my dream adorned
0	with what all earth or heaven could bestow
0	to make her amiable on she came 
0	led by her heavenly maker though unseen 
0	and guided by his voice nor uninformed
