0	i overjoyed could not forbear aloud 
0	this turn hath made amends thou hast fulfilled
0	thy words creator bounteous and benign 
0	giver of all things fair but fairest this
0	of all thy gifts nor enviest i now see
0	bone of my bone flesh of my flesh myself
0	before me woman is her name of man
0	extracted for this cause he shall forego
0	father and mother and to his wife adhere 
