0	what higher in her society thou findest
0	attractive human rational love still 
0	in loving thou dost well in passion not 
0	wherein true love consists not love refines
0	the thoughts and heart enlarges hath his seat
0	in reason and is judicious is the scale
0	by which to heavenly love thou mayest ascend 
0	not sunk in carnal pleasure for which cause 
0	among the beasts no mate for thee was found 
0	to whom thus half abashed adam replied 
0	neither her outside formed so fair nor aught
0	in procreation common to all kinds 
0	 though higher of the genial bed by far 
0	and with mysterious reverence i deem 
