0	yet these subject not i to thee disclose
0	what inward thence i feel not therefore foiled 
0	who meet with various objects from the sense
0	variously representing yet still free 
0	approve the best and follow what i approve 
0	to love thou blamest me not for love thou sayest 
0	leads up to heaven is both the way and guide 
0	bear with me then if lawful what i ask 
