0	venial discourse unblam d i now must change
0	those notes to tragick foul distrust and breach
0	disloyal on the part of man revolt 
0	and disobedience on the part of heaven
0	now alienated distance and distaste 
0	anger and just rebuke and judgement given 
0	that brought into this world a world of woe 
