0	easy my unpremeditated verse 
0	since first this subject for heroick song
0	pleas d me long choosing and beginning late 
0	not sedulous by nature to indite
0	wars hitherto the only argument
0	heroick deem d chief mastery to dissect
0	with long and tedious havock fabled knights
0	in battles feign d the better fortitude
0	of patience and heroick martyrdom
