0	till adam thus gan eve to dalliance move 
0	eve now i see thou art exact of taste 
0	and elegant of sapience no small part 
0	since to each meaning savour we apply 
0	and palate call judicious i the praise
0	yield thee so well this day thou hast purveyed 
0	much pleasure we have lost while we abstained
0	from this delightful fruit nor known till now
0	true relish tasting if such pleasure be
0	in things to us forbidden it might be wished 
0	for this one tree had been forbidden ten 
0	but come so well refreshed now let us play 
0	as meet is after such delicious fare 
0	for never did thy beauty since the day
0	i saw thee first and wedded thee adorned
0	with all perfections so inflame my sense
0	with ardour to enjoy thee fairer now
0	than ever bounty of this virtuous tree 
0	so said he and forbore not glance or toy
0	of amorous intent well understood
0	of eve whose eye darted contagious fire 
