0	this other served but to eternize woe 
0	till i provided death so death becomes
0	his final remedy and after life 
0	tried in sharp tribulation and refined
0	by faith and faithful works to second life 
0	waked in the renovation of the just 
0	resigns him up with heaven and earth renewed 
0	but let us call to synod all the blest 
0	through heaven s wide bounds from them i will not hide
