0	the almighty thus pronounced his sovran will 
0	o sons like one of us man is become
0	to know both good and evil since his taste
0	of that defended fruit but let him boast
0	his knowledge of good lost and evil got 
0	happier had it sufficed him to have known
0	good by itself and evil not at all 
