0	strength added from above new hope to spring
0	out of despair joy but with fear yet linked 
0	which thus to eve his welcome words renewed 
0	eve easily my faith admit that all
0	the good which we enjoy from heaven descends 
0	but that from us aught should ascend to heaven
0	so prevalent as to concern the mind
0	of god high blest or to incline his will 
0	hard to belief may seem yet this will prayer
0	or one short sigh of human breath upborne
0	even to the seat of god for since i sought
0	by prayer the offended deity to appease 
0	kneeled and before him humbled all my heart 
0	methought i saw him placable and mild 
0	bending his ear persuasion in me grew
0	that i was heard with favour peace returned
0	home to my breast and to my memory
