0	i never from thy side henceforth to stray 
0	where er our day s work lies though now enjoined
0	laborious till day droop while here we dwell 
0	what can be toilsome in these pleasant walks 
0	here let us live though in fallen state content 
0	so spake so wished much humbled eve but fate
0	subscribed not nature first gave signs impressed
0	on bird beast air air suddenly eclipsed 
