0	adam observed and with his eye the chase
0	pursuing not unmoved to eve thus spake 
0	o eve some further change awaits us nigh 
0	which heaven by these mute signs in nature shows
0	forerunners of his purpose or to warn
0	us haply too secure of our discharge
0	from penalty because from death released
