0	adam bowed low he kingly from his state
0	inclined not but his coming thus declared 
0	adam heaven s high behest no preface needs 
0	sufficient that thy prayers are heard and death 
0	then due by sentence when thou didst transgress 
0	defeated of his seisure many days
