0	heart struck with chilling gripe of sorrow stood 
0	that all his senses bound eve who unseen
0	yet all had heard with audible lament
0	discovered soon the place of her retire 
0	o unexpected stroke worse than of death 
0	must i thus leave thee paradise thus leave
0	thee native soil these happy walks and shades 
0	fit haunt of gods where i had hope to spend 
